pan style="font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">{!Class__c.Id}</span><br><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">(Just in case you can't remember your username in this org, it is {!Contact.Username__c}).</span></font><br><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please confirm with any other staff members that they are ready to help you.<br></b><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The Topic for this class is </span></font><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">{!Class__c.Project_Topic__c} </b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">and the content can be found here: </span></font><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">{!Class__c.Content_URL__c}.</b><br><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Have fun and keep the students keen.</span></font><br><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">On
