status of all the students is updated.&nbsp; This Class's record can be found here:</span></font><br><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">https://codeclub-nz.my.salesforce.com/{!Class__c.Id}.</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">...and don't forget to log your time in the Salesforce.org system. &nbsp;Here's a direct link to the activity record where you can log your time once you have signed in via Aloha</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#333333" face="SalesforceSans, ProximaNovaRegular, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);"><b>https://foundation.my.salesforce.com/apex/Volunteerforce1?sfdc.tabName=01r80000000Gzb4#/log-hours?log-step=3</b></span></font><br><br><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">If you haven't already got a Scratch account, then sign up&nbsp;here:&nbsp;</font><font color="#333333" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">https://scratch.mit.edu/ .&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">It's a bit like Trailhead - you need to log into your scratch account before you can save any work you do.</span><br><br><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Regards,</span></font><br><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Code Club Aotearoa and Salesforce New Zealand</span></font></div>]]></td>
